I '''Abraham "Bram" Stoker''' (8 Noviembre 1847 – 20 Abril 1912) metung yang Irish a nobelista ampong talasulat makuyad a salita (''short story writer'') a pikabalwan dili ngeni king kayang pamanyulat king nobelang Gothic ning 1897 a ''[[Dracula]]''. Anyang mabye ya, mas kilala re antimong personal a kasaup (''personal assistant'') ning artistang i [[Sir Henry Irving]] ampo ing mánibalang pangkalakal (''business manager'') ning [[Lyceum Theatre, London|Lyceum Theatre]] king London, a bandi nang Irving .

